9:
That's rare, isn't it?
...Its friends were the same, though.
Maybe that's normal in this forest?
14:
It's not moving at all... Are we scaring
it?
18:
No, I think it's the opposite. Hunting's
prohibited in these woods, so the
rabbits must be used to scientists
doing surveys.
20: I think it's just waiting for us to feed it.
29:
...No, it's not starving or anything! I
think it was just hoping for a snack...
34:
...All right, I think we're good for
today! Your ability to understand
animals is really helpful for this kind
of work.
38:
I can hear them, but it's not like I can
have a conversation with them or
anything.
40:
...But I guess my ability is useful
enough to help the Guild out here
and there.
45: Were you able to talk with Rufo?
52:
I don't know why, and I can't do it
anymore.
55:
I wish I could have talked with Rufo,
too.
59:
...Nobody back home thought like
you do.
67:
Not out in the countryside, no. They
thought I was creepy, if anything.
71: That's why Rufo was my only friend...
74:
Hold on... The tone of the animals'
voices just shifted. They seem
alarmed somehowâ€”
83:
D'oh, I missed! Maybe I should go
back to using a bow...
86:
What do you think you're doing?!
Hunting is prohibited in this forestâ€”
90:
You. That gun. Did that bastard give
it to you?
94:
It's the same as mine. Where'd you
get it?!
97:
...Huh? Stupid kid, what're you on
about...
99:
Oh yeah, that's right... They told me
this gun was cursed, or something.
101: Maybe I'll try it out on you?
126: It's okay now, Ryunon. We're here.
142:
B-but... They all told me the same
thing...
143:
They said I can't understand
animals... That I'm just a weirdo!
145:
...Thank you... If you think so, then I
guess it's okay...
146:
...You're my only friend in the world.
And I know we'll be together forever.
153:
Aww... Poor baby.
Looks like your dumb dog died
saving you.
169:
Don't worry, Ryunon. He's in the
Guild's custody now.
171:
...We don't know what's up with the
gun, though. It looks like he just
bought it from some random dealer
he didn't know the name of...
178:
...It wasn't supposed to be like this.
We were supposed to be together...
180:
Rufo was my first friend...
Whenever I'd start crying, Rufo
would never leave my side until I
stopped...
188:
...But then it all got ripped away from
me.
192:
That's why I'll kill that person...
They'll never hurt anyone again...
206:
You should get some more rest. You
still look tired.
215:
Tell us more about Rufo when you
wake up.
223:
I want to tell you all about Rufo, so...
please...
228:
Of course, Ryunon. We're looking
forward to it.
